<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 13:57:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>空对地能力已经渗透到 F-15EX 的任务中</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/air-to-ground-capabilities-are-already-creeping-into-the-f-15exs-mission-set</link><description>&lt;p&gt;F-15EX 目前的任务与其前身 F-15C 相同，都是严格的空对空作战，但这种情况将会改变。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/air-to-ground-capabilities-are-already-creeping-into-the-f-15exs-mission-set"&gt;空对地能力已经渗透到 F-15EX 的任务集中&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 23:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/air-to-ground-capabilities-are-already-creeping-into-the-f-15exs-mission-set</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装现在在红海袭击沙特油轮，对能源供应造成重大影响（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/houthis-now-attacking-saudi-oil-tankers-in-red-sea-major-energy-supply-implications</link><description>&lt;p&gt;就在与伊朗的战争即将再次全面爆发之际，胡塞武装将进一步挤压世界能源供应。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/houthis-now-attacking-saudi-oil-tankers-in-red-sea-major-energy-supply-implications"&gt;胡塞武装现在在红海袭击沙特油轮，对能源供应造成重大影响（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 23:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/houthis-now-attacking-saudi-oil-tankers-in-red-sea-major-energy-supply-implications</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰F-16首次空对空击落俄罗斯战斗机：美国高级将领</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ukrainian-f-16-scored-first-air-to-air-kill-against-a-russian-fighter-top-u-s-general</link><description>&lt;p&gt;丹·凯恩将军的披露证实了乌克兰 F-16 本月击落一架俄罗斯 Su-35S 的报道。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ukrainian-f-16-scored-first-air-to-air-kill-against-a-russian-fighter-top-u-s-general"&gt;乌克兰 F-16 对俄罗斯战斗机首次空对空击落：美国高级将军&lt;/a&gt;首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 18:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ukrainian-f-16-scored-first-air-to-air-kill-against-a-russian-fighter-top-u-s-general</guid></item><item><title>Brontanax 战斗机无人机是英国向协作战斗机迈出的一大步</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/brontanax-fighter-drone-is-the-uks-big-leap-into-collaborative-combat-aircraft</link><description>&lt;p&gt;BAE Systems 刚刚推出了具有一些有趣功能的隐形 CCA。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/brontanax-fighter-drone-is-the-uks-big-leap-into-collaborative-combat-aircraft"&gt;Brontanax 战斗机无人机是英国协作战斗机的大跃进，&lt;/a&gt;该文章首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 17:57:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/brontanax-fighter-drone-is-the-uks-big-leap-into-collaborative-combat-aircraft</guid></item><item><title>海军选择 RAACM-ER 低成本巡航导弹用于帮助武装盟友的计划（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-picks-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-for-program-to-help-arm-allies</link><description>&lt;p&gt;CHAOS计划旨在为友军地面部队提供新的、更便宜的方法来远距离攻击陆地上的船只和目标。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-picks-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-for-program-to-help-arm-allies"&gt;海军选择 RAACM-ER 低成本巡航导弹用于帮助武装盟友的计划（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 17:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-picks-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-for-program-to-help-arm-allies</guid></item><item><title>海军寻求母舰用于南方司令部行动</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/mothership-sought-by-navy-for-southern-command-operations</link><description>&lt;p&gt;该船将能够发射和回收直升机、无人机和小船，并充当海上行动基地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/mothership-sought-by-navy-for-southern-command-operations"&gt;海军为南方司令部行动寻找母舰后&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 16:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/mothership-sought-by-navy-for-southern-command-operations</guid></item><item><title>英国关注台风与配备流星导弹的 CCA 战斗机无人机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/typhoons-paired-with-cca-fighter-drones-armed-with-meteor-missiles-eyed-by-uk</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新兴概念设想台风在新雷达和下一代驾驶舱的帮助下指挥忠诚的僚机无人机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/typhoons-paired-with-cca-fighter-drones-armed-with-meteor-missiles-eyed-by-uk"&gt;英国关注的台风与配备流星导弹的 CCA 战斗机无人机配对的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 21:18:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/typhoons-paired-with-cca-fighter-drones-armed-with-meteor-missiles-eyed-by-uk</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争中的军火支出成为参议院听证会的焦点（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/munitions-expenditures-in-iran-war-take-center-stage-at-senate-hearing</link><description>&lt;p&gt;五角大楼希望拨款 21B 美元来更换已经使用的武器，因为这敲响了未来用可用弹药维持冲突的警钟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/munitions-expenditures-in-iran-war-take-center-stage-at-senate-hearing"&gt;伊朗战争中的军需开支在参议院听证会上成为焦点（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 19:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/munitions-expenditures-in-iran-war-take-center-stage-at-senate-hearing</guid></item><item><title>这艘新型诺斯罗普航天器可以使用其机械臂攻击敌方卫星吗？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/space/could-this-new-northrop-spacecraft-use-its-robotic-arms-to-attack-enemy-satellites</link><description>&lt;p&gt;任务机器人车辆的工作是维护轨道上的卫星并为其加油，但它也为另一种“武装”能力打开了大门。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/space/could-this-new-northrop-spacecraft-use-its-robotic-arms-to-attack-enemy-satellites"&gt;这篇新的诺斯罗普航天器可以使用其机械臂攻击敌方卫星吗？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 19:45:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/space/could-this-new-northrop-spacecraft-use-its-robotic-arms-to-attack-enemy-satellites</guid></item><item><title>狂怒忠诚僚机抵达克里奇空军基地进行敏捷作战部署试验</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/fury-loyal-wingman-arrives-at-creech-afb-for-agile-combat-deployment-trials</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国空军的两种 CCA，即 YFQ-44 Fury 和 YFQ-42 Dark Merlin，都将在内华达州南部的克里奇空军基地进行测试。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/fury-loyal-wingman-arrives-at-creech-afb-for-agile-combat-deployment-trials"&gt;狂怒忠诚僚机抵达克里奇空军基地进行敏捷作战部署试验后，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 18:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/fury-loyal-wingman-arrives-at-creech-afb-for-agile-combat-deployment-trials</guid></item></channel></rss>